message: Let me help you make your dreams come true
Hi Kdief, nice to make your acquaintance. What do you mean by that? What do you think what my dreams are?

Hi kaila. I just read your profile and saw that you are chasing dreams. Of course I don’t know about your dreams. But chasing dreams with such a beautiful girl must be very enjoyable. That’s why I sent you this message , like a bottle in the sea just wondering what would happen after. BTW I’m from France. I live in Metz a city in the east of France. I am a surgeon and I am single searching someone for a long term relationship

Hi 😊 Thank you for your kind message. Your metaphor with the bottle in the sea made me smile ✨ It’s nice to hear you're following your own path as well. Being a surgeon sounds like a big responsibility. I can imagine life must be busy but fulfilling. What kind of surgeon are you? Wishing you lots of success, both in life and in finding someone who shares your dreams and values 💫 Take care for now and lots of positive energy to France, Kaila
I’m the head of the department of gynaecological and oncological surgery in the hospital where I live Would you like to get acquainted and see where it leads?
awakennedsoul
Collage

In the rush of chasing dreams and deadlines, we forget the simplest truths. Your health is your true wealth, your peace is your power, and believing in yourself is a full-time job. It’s not always grand gestures we crave, but a warm laugh, a safe presence, and someone who truly gets us. A stable home, a kind soul, and a heart that chooses peace over chaos is what truly matters. So travel freely, feel deeply, and shine unapologetically. Don’t waste your energy worrying. Use it to bloom, to love, to rise. Because everything, eventually, will work out. Just keep going.
Hey! That collage really resonates with me, especially the part about choosing peace over chaos. What’s your favorite way to find that calm in daily life? 😊
As I didn’t get further answers after our first conversation I thought you were not interested and I’m surprised by your sudden message

Every day I’m struggling against chaos because I am a surgeon specialised in oncological surgery ￼ After a long day of work, I’m trying to rest my mind walking in my garden looking at flowers eating fruits directly from the tree. And I like to travel to beautiful countries discovering new cultures enjoying every day like if it was the last one I’m just missing someone by my side that could give me love and that I would love

Hey! I totally get why you'd think that, my village project has been keeping me offline more than usual lately. Your garden routine sounds so peaceful though, especially after those intense surgery days. What's your favorite fruit to pick straight from the tree?
Here where I live the fruits are seasonal In june I had strawberries and raspberries. After I had figs and plums and apricots. In a few weeks I will have apples
In September i will have grapes
It’s much different than what you can find in Bali
I saw on your last post that you wish someone to date you. You will have a lot of demand 😂

Your garden sounds like such a sweet escape after those intense surgeries! Those seasonal fruits must taste incredible fresh off the tree. What's your favorite way to enjoy the grapes when they come in September?
They are from a small size so I will press them and drink the fresh juice Do you want to come drink it with me?

That sounds delicious, fresh grape juice from your own garden? I might just have to take you up on that one day 😄 There’s something so grounding about living with the rhythm of the seasons. Here in Bali, it's more tropical abundance than slow ripening… but I miss that sense of time passing through fruit and soil. You know, I’ve been pouring a lot of my energy lately into creating. writing, capturing moments, building something of my own. I started a little Patreon where I share the more personal, quiet parts of that journey, the kind of things that don’t always make it to Instagram. Maybe you’d enjoy seeing that side of me too, it's art btw. not what you think! 🤪 and if it’s something you’d like to support, I’d be really grateful 🌸 But for now… I’ll imagine us clinking glasses over freshly pressed grape juice in September 🍇✨
How can I get to this little patreon

Aww that makes me smile ☺️. It’s a cozy little corner I’ve been slowly building where I share more intimate moments, thoughts, and behind-the-scenes of my creative life 🌿 You can find it here: https://www.patreon.com/Kailas_World. Would love to have you there if it feels right for you ❤️.
Get more from Kaila's World on Patreon
Done

Thank you so much for your kindness and support! it truly means the world to me 🧡. Every thoughtful message and gesture reminds me why I keep creating and sharing my little corner of life. Your presence and encouragement make this journey feel lighter, warmer, and more meaningful. With gratitude from Bali, Kaila 🌿✨😘
Hello sweetheart, how's ur weekend?
I’m enjoying my morning coffee
How is your weekend
Its a bit busy, doing this social project on a village here in Bali, so not that much time to chill. What's ur plan for the weekend
I will do some household chores and after enjoy the good weather playing golf
Your last post on patreon is reaching perfection. Aphrodite in Bali
That's cool, enjoy the golfing!
Thank u very much, I appreciate that
Send me some pictures of you golfing if you dont mind
How old are you?
I'm 24. Gonna nap a bit now, this village social project is killing me 😅
So young. The spring time of your life
Your message about springtime made me smile, there's something magical about how you see things. How has your weekend been?
I have been playing golf between two thunder and I was wondering what would have happened if I was 30 years younger and met you
I would have certainly felt in love with you and asked you to marry me
Your such a sweetheart 🥰 what do you value most in a woman you are attracted to?
I’m just a man so of course the external appearance is the first thing you’re attracted by but after the inner beauty is the most important but you can find it out only when you meet people
